# Design System - Retro Aesthetic

## Brand Identity

FeedbackFlow uses a **retro-modern aesthetic** - clean, bold, with a hint of nostalgia. Think developer tool meets vintage print design.

## Color Palette

**IMPORTANT**: Always use the project's existing system colors. Never introduce custom or new colors.

### Primary Colors (CSS Variables)

```css
--retro-paper: #f7f5f0;    /* Background, cards */
--retro-black: #1a1a1a;    /* Text, borders, primary buttons */
--retro-yellow: #f3c952;   /* Accents, highlights, brand */
--retro-red: #e85d52;      /* Errors, high priority, bugs */
--retro-blue: #6b9ac4;     /* Links, info, active states */
--retro-lavender: #d4c4e8; /* Secondary accents, tags */
--retro-peach: #f4a261;    /* Warnings, medium priority */
--bg-page: #e8e6e1;        /* Page background */
```

### Tailwind Usage

```html
<div class="bg-retro-paper text-retro-black border-retro-black">
<span class="text-retro-red">Bug</span>
<span class="text-retro-blue">Feature</span>
```

### Status Colors

```css
--status-new: var(--retro-blue);
--status-triaging: var(--retro-yellow);
--status-drafted: var(--retro-lavender);
--status-exported: var(--stone-400);
--status-resolved: #22c55e;
```

## Typography

- **Primary font**: Inter (UI text)
- **Mono font**: JetBrains Mono (code, IDs, technical info)

```html
<span class="font-sans">Regular text</span>
<span class="font-mono text-xs">#FF-402</span>
```

## The Retro Box Pattern

Signature look uses **thick borders** and **offset shadows**:

```html
<!-- Standard card -->
<div class="border-2 border-retro-black bg-white shadow-retro">
  Content
</div>

<!-- Interactive card with hover -->
<div class="border-2 border-retro-black bg-white hover-card">
  Clickable content
</div>

<!-- Large shadow variant -->
<div class="border-2 border-retro-black shadow-retro-lg">
  Hero element
</div>
```

### Shadow Utilities (defined in globals.css)

- `shadow-retro` - 4px offset
- `shadow-retro-lg` - 8px offset  
- `shadow-retro-sm` - 2px offset
- `hover-card` - Interactive with hover effect

## Badges & Tags

```html
<!-- Priority badges -->
<span class="rounded border px-1.5 py-0.5 text-[10px] font-bold tracking-wider uppercase
  text-retro-red bg-retro-red/10 border-retro-red/20">High Priority</span>

<!-- Type badges -->
<span class="text-retro-red bg-retro-red/10">Bug</span>
<span class="text-retro-blue bg-retro-blue/10">Feature</span>
```

## Icons

Use **Solar Icons** via Iconify or lucide-react:

```tsx
import { Icon } from "@iconify/react";
<Icon icon="solar:camera-linear" width={24} />

// Or lucide-react
import { Camera, Bug, Lightbulb } from "lucide-react";
```

### Common Icons

| Purpose    | Solar Icon                    |
| ---------- | ----------------------------- |
| Screenshot | `solar:camera-linear`         |
| Record     | `solar:record-linear`         |
| Bug        | `solar:bug-linear`            |
| Feature    | `solar:lightbulb-linear`      |
| AI         | `solar:magic-stick-3-linear`  |
| Settings   | `solar:settings-linear`       |
| Export     | `solar:export-linear`         |
| Search     | `solar:magnifer-linear`       |

## Responsive Breakpoints

```css
sm: 640px   /* Tablet */
md: 768px   /* Tablet landscape */
lg: 1024px  /* Desktop */
xl: 1280px  /* Large desktop */
```

Dashboard sidebar hides on mobile, detail panel hides below lg.
